### Rust / Cargo ###
# Ignore Cargo build directory
/target/

# Ignore incremental compilation files
/**/target/

# If you want to commit Cargo.lock for reproducible builds (recommended for binaries),
# keep it. Otherwise uncomment the following line to ignore it for libraries.
# Cargo.lock

### Generated shader outputs ###
# Vertex/Fragment shaders generated by the transpiler
*.vert
*.frag

### Plugin artifacts (dynamic libraries produced by plugin crates)
# Usually under target/ but sometimes copied elsewhere by build scripts
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll

### Editor / OS files ###
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

### Temporary / logs ###
*.log
.env

### Rust tooling ###
# Rust analyzer cache
/rust-project.json
/.vscode/.rust-analyzer*

### Tests / local runtime outputs ###
# Ignore generated files placed next to test sources
/examples/*.vert
/examples/*.frag

### Misc ###
# Ignore coverage and profiling outputs
coverage/
*.prof
